      "type": "simple",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "While wearing the mask, you gain darkvision out to 60 feet. Once per long rest, you can activate its magic to become invisible for up to 1 hour or until you attack or cast a spell. You can speak the mask’s command word (in Old Rokugan dialect) as a bonus action.",
